function ReloadComments(n){$.ajax({url:"/api/post/comments?postId="+n,success:function(t){$.each(t,function(t,i){$("div.comments-body-"+n).append($("<div/>").html(`<div class="row p-2 my-2 border">
                                                <div class="my-2">
                                                    <p class="m-0">${i.creatorUserName}</p>
                                                    <sub>${i.createdOn}</sub>
                                                </div>
                                                <p class="px-4">${i.content}</p>
                                            </div>`))})},error:function(n){console.log(n)},beforeSend:function(){$("div.loader").show()},complete:function(){$("div.loader").hide();$("div.comments-body-"+n).show()},type:"GET",dataType:"json"})}$("#add-comment").click(function(n){n.preventDefault();var i=$(this).attr("action"),r=$(this).attr("method"),t=$(this).serialize();$.ajax({url:i,contentType:"application/text",data:t,type:r,dataType:"text",error:function(n){console.log(n)},success:function(){console.log("good");ReloadComments(t.postId)}})});$("a#like").click(function(){var n=$(this).attr("post-like-id");$.ajax({url:"api/post/like?postId="+n,success:function(){console.log("bad")},error:function(n){console.log(n)},complete:function(){console.log("good");$("a[post-like-Id="+n+"]").removeClass("btn-outline-success").addClass("btn-outline-danger");$("a[post-like-Id="+n+"] i").removeClass("far").addClass("fas");$("a[post-like-Id="+n+"]").attr("id","unlike")},type:"GET",dataType:"json"})});$("a#unlike").click(function(){var n=$(this).attr("post-like-id");$.ajax({url:"api/post/unlike?postId="+n,success:function(){console.log("bad")},error:function(n){console.log(n)},complete:function(){console.log("good");$("a[post-like-Id="+n+"]").removeClass("btn-outline-danger").addClass("btn-outline-success");$("a[post-like-Id="+n+"] i").removeClass("fas").addClass("far");$("a[post-like-Id="+n+"]").attr("id","like")},type:"GET",dataType:"json"})});$("a#comment-toggle").click(function(){var n=$(this).attr("post-id");$("div#comment-controls-"+n).show();$("div.comments-body-"+n).text("");ReloadComments(n)});